These are Puzzles for 4x3 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-1-1::.
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: ritmeester, bongani, prince
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: december, april, july
The people have 3 different hobbies: chess, sudoku, woodworking
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: blues, folk, reggae
1. the person who's birthday is in april is the bongani-smoker##1
2. the fan of reggae is on the far left##1
3. the prince-smoker is on the left of the fan of blues##1
4. the person who's hobby is chess is the person who's birthday is in july##1
5. the person who's birthday is in december is in the middle##1
6. the prince-smoker is the person who's birthday is in july##1
7. the person who's hobby is woodworking is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |      2      |     3     |
| Cigar      | prince  | ritmeester       | bongani   |
| Birthday          | july | december | april |
| Hobby         | chess  | woodworking | sudoku    |
| Music-Genre   | reggae | blues       | folk      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-1-2::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: coffee, 7up, water
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: fonseca, dunhill, alhambra
There are 3 different nationalities: brazilian, italian, turkish
3 different pets are kept: hedgehog, rat, snake
1. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the person drinking 7up##1
2. the person drinking water is on the right of the owner of the rat##1
3. the fonseca-smoker is on the right of the italian##1
4. the alhambra-smoker is on the left of the dunhill-smoker##1
5. the owner of the snake is on the far left##1
6. the owner of the snake is the brazilian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |       3       |
| Beverage          | coffee      | 7up  | water        |
| Cigar         | alhambra | dunhill | fonseca |
| Nationality   | brazilian | italian | turkish       |
| Pet           | snake     | rat     | hedgehog      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-1-3::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, coffee, mirinda
3 different pets are kept: turtle, dog, goldfish
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: adventure, satire, zombie
House: cape-cod, art-deco, townhouse
1. the owner of the goldfish is the cape-cod house##1
2. the art-deco house is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1
3. the owner of the dog is on the left of the cape-cod house##1
4. the person watching zombie movies is in the middle##1
5. the person watching adventure movies is on the left of the owner of the goldfish##1
6. the person drinking mirinda is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |         2          |    3    |
| Beverage      | coffee    | almond-milk        | mirinda |
| Pet           | dog    | goldfish | turtle    |
| Movie-Genre   | adventure | zombie             | satire  |
| House     | townhouse     | cape-cod                | art-deco  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-1-4::.
There 3 different types of food: pear, pepper, tomato
House: victorian, futuristic, craftsman
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: drama, horror, western
City: boston, edinburgh, paris
1. the person traveling to paris is on the right of the person traveling to edinburgh##1
2. the person eating tomato is on the left of the futuristic house##1
3. the person traveling to boston is on the left of the person watching horror movies##1
4. the person eating pear is the person traveling to paris##1
5. the person watching drama movies is on the right of the victorian house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |     3     |
| Food          | pepper    | tomato  | pear      |
| House           | craftsman    | victorian | futuristic |
| Movie-Genre   | western   | horror  | drama     |
| City   | boston | edinburgh    | paris      |

