.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-1-5::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: cooking, singing, video-games
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: soccer, snowboarding, cricket
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: salsa, pop, dubstep
3 different pets are kept: dog, hedgehog, lizard
1. the fan of salsa is the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
2. the owner of the hedgehog is on the right of the person who's hobby is cooking##1
3. the person who's sport is cricket is the person who's hobby is video-games##1
4. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the far left##1
5. the owner of the dog is the person who's hobby is cooking##1
6. the fan of dubstep is the person who's sport is soccer##1
7. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the left of the person who's hobby is singing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2      |     3     |
| Hobby         | video-games | cooking     | singing   |
| Sport           | cricket       | snowboarding   | soccer     |
| Music-Genre   | pop     | salsa | dubstep |
| Pet           | lizard      | dog         | hedgehog  |

