.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-1-6::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: singing, fishing, rock-climbing
There are 3 different favourite colors: black, purple, yellow
3 different pets are kept: ferret, frog, rat
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: sailing, snowboarding, tennis
1. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the right of the person who likes black##1
2. the owner of the ferret is in the middle##1
3. the person who likes yellow is on the far left##1
4. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the left of the person who's sport is tennis##1
5. the owner of the frog is on the left of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2       |    3    |
| Hobby          | singing | fishing       | rock-climbing |
| Color   | yellow     | black       | purple   |
| Pet           | frog      | ferret       | rat     |
| Sport         | sailing   | snowboarding | tennis  |

