.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-1-7::.
There 3 different types of food: broccoli, cherry, plum
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: marigold, zinnia, bellflower
There are 3 different favourite beverages: coffee, juice, hot-chocolate
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: funk, metal, pop
1. the fan of metal is on the far left##1
2. the person who growszinnia is on the right of the person eating cherry##1
3. the person who growsbellflower is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1
4. the person eating broccoli is on the right of the fan of funk##1
5. the fan of pop is on the right of the person drinking juice##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |       2        |     3      |
| Food          | plum       | cherry         | broccoli   |
| Flower           | marigold | bellflower | zinnia |
| Beverage   | coffee     | juice        | hot-chocolate        |
| Music-Genre   | metal      | funk           | pop        |

