The people have 3 different jobs:  pilot, doctor, mechanic
1. the pilot is on the far right##1
2. the owner of the rabbit is the mechanic##1
3. the person who's hobby is woodworking is in the middle##1
4. the indonesian is on the left of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
5. the owner of the rabbit is on the left of the colombian##1
6. the pilot is the owner of the fish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |      3       |
