.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-1-9::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: chess, cooking, writing
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: volleyball, soccer, handball
3 different pets are kept: goat, goldfish, guinea-pig
3 different games are played: poker, canasta, whist
1. the person playing whist is in the middle##1
2. the owner of the goldfish is on the far right##1
3. the person who's hobby is cooking is the person playing canasta##1
4. the person who's sport is volleyball is the owner of the guinea-pig##1
5. the person who's sport is handball is on the far left##1
6. the person who's hobby is writing is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |         1          |     2      |    3     |
| Hobby       | cooking            | chess      | writing  |
| Sport         | handball | volleyball | soccer |
| Pet         | goat               | guinea-pig | goldfish |
| Game   | canasta             | whist       | poker      |

