.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-1-10::.
The people use 3 different means of transport: bike, scooter, motorbike
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: epic, martial-arts, mystery
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: climbing, ice-hockey, tennis
3 different pets are kept: bird, goat, lizard
1. the person watching martial-arts movies is the owner of the goat##1
2. the owner of the lizard is on the far left##1
3. the owner of the bird is on the right of the owner of the goat##1
4. the person driving the scooter is on the far right##1
5. the person driving the bike is on the left of the person who's sport is tennis##1
6. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the left of the person watching mystery movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2       |      3      |
| Transport           | motorbike | bike         | scooter |
| Movie-Genre   | epic      | martial-arts | mystery     |
| Sport   | climbing   | ice-hockey       | tennis     |
| Pet           | lizard    | goat         | bird        |

