The people use 3 different means of transport: boat, bus, helicopter
1. the person traveling to paris is on the right of the journalist##1
2. the videographer is on the right of the person who growsdaffodil##1
3. the videographer is on the right of the person driving the helicopter##1
4. the person driving the bus is on the left of the person traveling to boston##1
5. the person traveling to boston is on the right of the videographer##1
6. the person who growslily is on the left of the person who growsbellflower##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |     3     |
| Job           | journalist | videographer | architect |
| Flower   | daffodil        | lily       | bellflower     |
| City   | san-francisco     | paris         | boston     |
| Transport     | helicopter | bus          | boat      |

