.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-1-12::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  architect, paramedic, dressmaker
There are 3 different favourite colors: black, lavender, aquamarine
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: folk, gospel, rock
3 different pets are kept: hamster, hedgehog, horse
1. the owner of the horse is the fan of gospel##1
2. the person who likes lavender is on the far left##1
3. the architect is on the right of the person who likes black##1
4. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left of the paramedic##1
5. the owner of the horse is on the left of the fan of folk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |       2       |      3      |
| Job      | dressmaker    | paramedic | architect |
| Color   | lavender | black     | aquamarine     |
| Music-Genre   | rock        | gospel        | folk        |
| Pet           | hedgehog    | horse         | hamster     |

