.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-1-13::.
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: february, april, november
3 different games are played: monopoly, go, chess
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: dubstep, metal, punk
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: badminton, cricket, sailing
1. the person who's sport is sailing is the person who's birthday is in february##1
2. the fan of punk is on the left of the person who's sport is badminton##1
3. the person who's birthday is in april is on the left of the fan of punk##1
4. the person who's birthday is in november is the person playing go##1
5. the fan of punk is on the left of the fan of dubstep##1
6. the person playing chess is on the left of the person who's sport is sailing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2    |     3     |
| Birthday         | april | february | november   |
| Game           | chess     | monopoly    | go   |
| Music-Genre   | metal         | punk    | dubstep   |
| Sport         | cricket       | sailing | badminton |

