3. the person eating strawberry is on the right of the person who growsorchid##1
4. the siglo-smoker is on the left of the person eating lime##1
5. the havana-smoker is the person who growsrose##1
6. the person who growsmarigold is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |     2      |     3      |
| Cigar    | siglo | game     | havana      |
| Food        | garlic | lime       | strawberry |
| Hobby       | sudoku | collecting | traveling  |
| Flower   | marigold    | orchid   | rose  |

