The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: animation, drama, disaster
1. the person watching animation movies is on the far right##1
2. the person eating kale is on the right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
3. the person watching drama movies is the person who's sport is swimming##1
4. the person who's sport is swimming is on the far left##1
5. the person drinking almond-milk is in the middle##1
6. the person eating peas is the person drinking iced-tea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |      2      |     3      |
| Beverage      | iced-tea | almond-milk | cola       |
| Food          | peas     | artichoke   | kale       |
| Sport         | swimming  | snowboarding   | rowing |
| Movie-Genre   | drama   | disaster       | animation  |

