.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-1-19::.
There 3 different types of food: pear, grapefruit, kale
The people have 3 different jobs:  journalist, lawyer, kalecher
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: dubstep, reggae, salsa
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: family, drama, animation
1. the fan of reggae is on the left of the person watching family movies##1
2. the kalecher is on the left of the person watching drama movies##1
3. the person eating kale is the person watching family movies##1
4. the fan of reggae is the person eating grapefruit##1
5. the lawyer is on the left of the person watching family movies##1
6. the person watching animation movies is on the left of the fan of salsa##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2    |     3      |
| Food      | grapefruit         | kale     | pear     |
| Job           | lawyer        | kalecher | journalist |
| Music-Genre   | reggae        | salsa   | dubstep    |
| Movie-Genre         | animation | family   | drama |

