.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-1-20::.
3 different games are played: billiard, scrabble, bridge
The people have 3 different hobbies: collecting, hiking, traveling
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: classical, folk, r&b
There are 3 different favourite beverages: juice, fanta, coffee
1. the person playing bridge is on the far left##1
2. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the left of the person playing billiard##1
3. the fan of r&b is on the right of the person drinking fanta##1
4. the person drinking juice is on the far left##1
5. the person drinking fanta is in the middle##1
6. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the left of the fan of folk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |     3      |
| Game          | bridge     | scrabble    | billiard    |
| Hobby         | collecting | traveling | hiking     |
| Music-Genre   | classical  | folk      | r&b        |
| Beverage         | juice   | fanta   | coffee |

 